<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">“<span style="font-size: 18px;">日出江花红胜火，春来江水绿如蓝”，生机勃勃的春天，鸟语花香的春天，一幅幅美如画的景象出现在我们的面前。为丰富校园文化生活，提升我院学子的审美情趣，展现我院师生与花朵之间的和谐之美，传递自然与人文的交融之情，经济管理学院开展“花间仙子，镜映自然”主题摄影比赛！</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">摄影作品</span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712839124508003015.png" title="1712839124508003015.png" alt="image.png" width="471" height="360" style="width: 471px; height: 360px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220508杨静 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712839186847072451.png" title="1712839186847072451.png" alt="image.png" width="462" height="382" style="width: 462px; height: 382px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">C230516董欣怡 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712839337405083892.png" title="1712839337405083892.png" alt="image.png" width="462" height="342" style="width: 462px; height: 342px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230505万俊豪 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240515/1715753568969096780.png" title="1715753568969096780.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p>